# Investigation Report: PhoneHub "Car Brands" Display Bug

## Objective
Investigate the reported bug where the "car brands" section shows phone amounts instead of appropriate car brand information, and produce a fix plan focused on simplicity and maintainability.

---

## Exploration Summary

### 1. Site Structure

The main website lives at `c:\Users\96650\OneDrive\Desktop\AI_BA_WORKSPACE\phonehub\` with this structure:

