- (Option B) Add type grouping similar to brands.html

Recommended: **Option A** -- filter to brands whose `primaryCategory` is "phone", since the homepage is the primary landing page and should focus on phones.

**File**: `c:\Users\96650\OneDrive\Desktop\AI_BA_WORKSPACE\phonehub\js\home.js`

