Lines 42-44 currently render ALL brands as filter checkboxes. Consider grouping by type or hiding car brands when the user is filtering phones.

**File**: `c:\Users\96650\OneDrive\Desktop\AI_BA_WORKSPACE\phonehub\js\search.js`

